import React,{useContext,useEffect,useState} from 'react' import '../styles/BookingSummary.css' import flightContent from "../context/FlightContext"; import '../styles/BookingSummary.css' const BookingSummary = () => { const content = useContext(flightContent) const {selectedflight, adultCounter, childCounter,infantCounter ,passCount,localpassengers,departDate,passengersinfo, setPassengersinfo,setSelectedflight} = content useEffect(() => { setSelectedflight(JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('selectedflight'))) setPassengersinfo(JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('passengersinfo'))) }, []) return (
Trip summary
{selectedflight.map((flight)=>{ return
Outbound flight
{flight.departure}
→
{flight.destination}
{departDate}
Departure
Arrival
Operated by
Class
{flight.departuretime+' '+flight.departurecode}
{flight.destinationtime+' '+flight.destinationcode}
{flight.flightname}
Economy
{flight.departure+', '+flight.departureairport}
Non-stop
{flight.destination+', '+flight.destinationairport}
})}
Passenger Details
Passenger name
Passport
Date of birth
Type
{passengersinfo.map((element)=>{ const {firstname,lastname,passport,type} = element return <>
{firstname.replace(firstname.charAt(0), firstname.charAt(0).toUpperCase())+' '+lastname.replace(lastname.charAt(0), lastname.charAt(0).toUpperCase())}
{passport?passport:'-'}
-
{type}
})}
{/*
Passenger name
Type
Email
Number
{localpassengers.map((element)=>{ const {firstname,lastname,passport,type} = element return <>
{firstname.replace(firstname.charAt(0), firstname.charAt(0).toUpperCase())+' '+lastname.replace(lastname.charAt(0), lastname.charAt(0).toUpperCase())}
{passport?passport:'-'}
-
{type}
})}
*/}
{/*
Total trip price:
{adultCounter?<>{adultCounter} Adult:''}{childCounter?<>+{childCounter}Child:''}{infantCounter?<>+{infantCounter}Infant:''}
{passCount}
*/}
) } export default BookingSummary
